products.description: Cast your mind to the end of 2020; do you remember Balenciaga's Fall '21 collection taking the form of a video game? It was the first time a fashion brand had ever presented playable software. Continuing Demna Gvasalia's obsession with gaming, the house has dropped a sought after capsule collection in collaboration with PlayStation. Paying homage to the sold out PS5 console, this oversized cotton jersey hoody is cloaked in dual branding.Balenciaga cotton jersey hoody100% cottonSlips onHood, dropped shoulders, long sleeves, branded text print at front, sleeves and back, kangaroo pocket at front, oversized fit, ribbed trimsHand washMade in PortugalThis style runs large. For those who are in between sizes, we suggest you go one size downSize small: length 28in / 71cmModel is 5ft 11in/1.80m and wears a size smallMidweight, slight stretch
products.name: Balenciaga x PlayStation graphic-print cotton-jersey hoody

products.description: Demna Gvasalia, of Balenciaga, can be credited for leading the fray when reinventing modern, utilitarian garments - and the same goes for its footwear. The Strike ankle boots couldn't have come at a better time, complete with a chunky platform that would challenge even the boldest of protestors. Carved from croc embossed leather, this tonal pair is set on a toothed rubber outsole making for the sturdiest pair by the Spanish house, yet.Balenciaga croc embossed leather platform ankle bootsDetails:Lace up fasteningClosed, round toeMid calf heightTone on tone lacesVisible, tone on tone top stitching8 eyelets lace up vampThick, toothed outsoleLoop at backMade in ItalyFabric:Upper: 100% leatherLining: 100% leatherSole: 100% rubberSize & Fit:Heel height 1.75"Platform height 1"Care:Wipe with a soft cloth
products.name: Balenciaga Strike croc-embossed leather platform ankle boots, Size: EUR 36 / 3 UK WOMEN
